==== SOURCE

https://www.forbes.com/sites/amitchowdhry/2014/03/18/facebooks-deepface-software-can-match-faces-with-97-25-accuracy/

==== AGENT

Facebook DeepFace

==== GOAL

Identify people from a picture.

==== DATA

They used images from Facebook users.

==== METHODS

They used 4 million images of up to 4000 people to train

==== RESULTS

Facebook is able to detect wether a person in two images are the same or not irrespective
of the camera angle and lighting with 97.25% accuracy.

==== COMMENTS

Facebook has been able to correctly identify people in my facebook account. It works really well.